<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.2),rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url(https://howchoo.com/media/od/q4/ng/30-of-the-best-video-game-storylines.png?width=1440&auto=webp&quality=70);">
</div>
<%= render 'offers/category_buttons' %>
<div class="container text-center">
  <p>We have a vast selection of games to choose from. Trust us that you can find any game you could possibly want! Just select a game and set your rental period. Prices are per day and durations can be extended at any time. If you have a game you want to rent out check out our rentals page!</p>
</div>
<div class="container pt-3">
  <h4 class="d-flex justify-content-center"></h4>
  <div class='container cards'>
    <% @offers.each do |offer| %>
      <div class="card-trip mb-5">
        <%= image_tag offer.video_game.image_url, alt: offer.video_game.title %>
        <div>
          <div class="card-trip-infos">
            <div>
              <h2 class="d-inline-block text-truncate" style="max-width: 200px"><strong><%= offer.video_game.title.upcase %></strong></h2>
              <p class='mb-2'><strong><%= offer.video_game.category %></strong></p>
              <p class='mb-2'><strong>Released: <%= offer.video_game.publishing_year %></strong></p>
              <h5 class="card-trip-pricing"><strong>Â¥<%= offer.price %></strong></h5>
              <%= link_to "", offer_path(offer), class: "card-link"  %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
